---
title: GeoModeler3D — Animation Player State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Stopped

    Stopped --> Playing : Play()
    Playing --> Paused : Pause()
    Paused --> Playing : Play() / resume
    Playing --> Stopped : Stop() / reset to t=0
    Paused --> Stopped : Stop() / reset to t=0
    Playing --> Stopped : reached Duration AND NOT IsLooping
    Playing --> Playing : reached Duration AND IsLooping / reset to t=0

    state Playing {
        [*] --> Ticking
        Ticking --> Ticking : DispatcherTimer fires then advance time then EvaluateAll then raise FrameTick
    }
